<TEXT>
Sir, Your leading article, 'Paying for parties (April 14), on the report of
the home affairs select committee on the funding of political parties,
claims that the Labour minority called for state funding. It then goes on to
criticise us for doing so.
In fact our minority report makes no reference to state funding except to
