 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Chargeable gains              14,800      9,800
Allowable losses
(excluding indexation
losses from Nov 1993          -2,000     12,800
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Annual exemption
assume unchanged
for 1994/95                   -5,800     -5,800
Taxable gains                  7,000      4,000
before relief                  7,000      4,000
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Indexation losses
(ie losses attributable
to indexation)
on sales
from Nov 30 to April 5:       12,000
Relieved in 1993/94           -7,000
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Indexation losses
on sales 1994/95:              6,000
Add unrelieved
1993/94:
12,000 - 7,000                 5,000
                              11,000
Limited to max                10,000
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
