<HEADLINE>
FT  16 APR 94 / UK Company News: Fiscal ends first day at 3p discount
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Fiscal Properties' shares closed at 75p on their first day of trading
yesterday, compared with the issue price of 78p. A total of 20.54m shares
had been sold through a placing and intermediaries offer. Turnover yesterday
was 385,000 shares.
