pro-forma sales of SKr27.4bn, would also be seeking a listing in the US.
There had been talk of the sell-off being postponed due to worries about the
size of the offer, and unsettled market conditions.
Volvo is Pharmacia's other main shareholder, with a 28 per cent stake.
Antonia Sharpe adds: Pharmacia plans to access the syndicated loan market
with a Dollars 500m five-year revolving credit facility. JP Morgan and Union
Bank of Switzerland will act as joint arrangers.
